    "|----------|------|---------------|\n",
    "| Distance | Å (Ångström) | $10^{-10}$ m |\n",
    "| Mass | amu (unified atomic mass unit) | $1.66054 \\times 10^{-27}$ kg |\n",
    "| Time | fs (femtosecond) | $10^{-15}$ s |\n",
    "| Energy | kcal/mol | $4184 / N_A$ J per particle |\n",
    "| Force | kcal/(mol·Å) | — |\n",
    "| Temperature | K (Kelvin) | — |\n",
    "| Charge | $e$ (elementary charge) | $1.602 \\times 10^{-19}$ C |\n",
    "\n",
    "From these base units, the following derived constants appear throughout the framework:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Boltzmann constant:**\n",
    "$$\n",
    "k_B = 0.001987204 \\; \\text{kcal/(mol·K)}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "This is $R / N_A = 8.31446 / (4184) \\times 1000$ kcal/(mol·K). It appears in temperature computation, velocity initialization, and thermostat equations.\n",
    "\n",
