    "## 4.3 Velocity Initialization\n",
    "\n",
    "At the start of a molecular dynamics run, velocities must be drawn from the Maxwell-Boltzmann distribution at the target temperature. Each Cartesian component of each particle's velocity is sampled independently from a Gaussian:\n",
