    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "The width $\\sigma_v = \\sqrt{k_B T / m_i}$ is mass-dependent: heavy atoms move slower. For hydrogen at 300 K, $\\sigma_v \\approx 0.024$ Å/fs; for carbon, $\\sigma_v \\approx 0.007$ Å/fs.\n",
