    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf{v}_\\text{COM} = \\frac{\\sum_i m_i \\mathbf{v}_i}{\\sum_i m_i}, \\qquad \\mathbf{v}_i \\leftarrow \\mathbf{v}_i - \\mathbf{v}_\\text{COM}\n",
