    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "S = \\frac{V}{1 + \\lambda C} \\times 50\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "where $V = w_N \\cdot w_Q \\cdot w_M \\cdot w_D \\cdot w_S \\cdot w_C$ is the scientific value and $C$ is a normalized computational cost.\n",
    "\n",
