    "\n",
    "| Factor | Formula | What it measures |\n",
    "|--------|---------|------------------|\n",
    "| $w_N$ | Dual Gaussian peaks at $N=8$ and $N=56$ | Size preference (small molecules + medium clusters) |\n",
    "| $w_Q$ | $e^{-k|\\sum q_i|}$ with $k=2$ | Charge neutrality |\n",
    "| $w_M$ | $1 + 0.3 \\cdot (N_\\text{metal}/N)$ | Metal content |\n",
    "| $w_D$ | $1 + 0.5 \\cdot (n_\\text{unique}/\\ln(1+N))$ | Element diversity |\n",
